[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0199","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0199.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0084","title":"多款 NFS 服务器权限提升漏洞","description":"某些 NFS 服务器存在权限提升漏洞，由于未对 `mknod` 系统调用进行有效的权限检查，普通用户可通过 `mknod` 创建可写的 `/dev/kmem` 设备文件，并将自身 UID 设置为 0（root），从而获得内核内存的读写访问权限，实现本地权限提升至 root。该漏洞影响多个 NFS 服务实现，攻击者需拥有本地用户账户，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0084"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1990-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.553","remediation":"升级至 NFS v4.1.3 或更高版本以修复 mknod 权限提升漏洞。在客户端挂载 NFS 共享时务必使用 `nosuid` 和 `nodev` 选项，禁止设备文件创建和 SUID 可执行；服务端导出目录时启用 `root_squash` 将 root 用户映射为匿名用户，并严格限制 exports 权限为只读（`ro`）而非读写（`rw`），同时移除不必要的 writable kmem 设备访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/78"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0199.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0195","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0195.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0082","title":"FTPD CWD ~root 命令权限提升漏洞","description":"FTP 守护进程（ftpd）在处理 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令时存在路径遍历缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过发送特制的 `CWD ~root` 指令将当前工作目录切换至 root 用户家目录，从而绕过文件访问限制获取超级用户权限，实现对目标服务器的完全控制。该漏洞无需任何认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0082"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1988-11-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.300","remediation":"升级 ftpd 至厂商最后发布的修复版本（如 wu-ftpd 2.6.2+、ProFTPD 1.2.0rc2+），禁用匿名用户的 CWD 命令或限制 `~root` 路径解析；如无法升级，关闭 FTP 服务并迁移至 SFTP/SCP 替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.alw.nih.gov/Security/Docs/admin-guide-to-cracking.101.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0195.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0223","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0223.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0095","title":"Berkeley Sendmail Debug 命令远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Sendmail 5.58 及更早版本中默认启用了调试（debug）命令功能，远程攻击者可通过 SMTP 端口向目标发送特制的 debug 命令，以 root 权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Berkeley Sendmail 邮件服务器，无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级严重。厂商已发布补丁禁用调试功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0095"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1988-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.460","remediation":"立即将 Sendmail 升级至 8.6.x 或更高版本，该系列已默认禁用 debug/wizard 调试命令。如无法升级，在 sendmail.cf 配置文件中添加 Ow 选项（即 O Wizard=no）以关闭 wiz 模式。在网络层面限制对 TCP 端口 25 的访问，仅允许可信来源连接 SMTP 服务作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2019/Jun/16","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/05/4","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/06/1","http://www.osvdb.org/195","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19028","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0095.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0095","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/1999/CVE-1999-0095.rules","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/Mishthi27/SentrySense2.0/blob/de64bcf93503f6469484cdfdd5c26732e8f3f623/predictive_ai/threats/CVE-1999-0095.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0095.json","https://github.com/trailofbits/cb-multios/blob/810d7b24b1f62f56ef49b148fe155b0d0629cad2/challenges/REMATCH_1--Hat_Trick--Morris_Worm/README.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c